      "title": "Shooting in Sri Lanka\u2019s South: Two dead",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Colombo (News 1st): Two people were gunned down at a hotel in Ambalangoda on Sunday (21) evening.",
        "Sri Lanka Police said that the shooting took place at an upper floor of a hotel located in Delduwa, Ambalangoda.",
        "No further details were available about the shooter or shooters, or the motive for the shooting.",
        "World Bank impose strict regulations for fertilizer imports \u2013 Report"
